  <title>Diálogo de pergunta</title>
      <p>
          Use the <cmd>--question</cmd> option to create a question dialog.
      </p>

      <p>
        The following example script shows how to create a question dialog:
      </p>

<code>
#!/bin/bash

zenity --question \
--text="Are you sure you wish to proceed?"
</code>


